<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head') %>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/three.js/r128/three.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="three-bg"></div>

    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <main>
        <!-- HERO -->
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="hero-content">
                    <span class="badge">✦ Mindset.i</span>
                    <h1>
                        Inspire change.<br>
                        <span class="highlight">Awaken potential.</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p class="subtitle">"All that you are looking for is at the place you are looking from."</p>
                    <p class="quote">Change begins in one place — the individual. Not the system. Not the crowd. Not tomorrow. Here. Now. In me.</p>
                    <div class="hero-buttons">
                        <a href="/services" class="btn-primary">Explore Our Services</a>
                        <a href="/about" class="btn-secondary">Our Philosophy</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="scroll-indicator">
                    <span>Scroll to explore</span>
                    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- THE SEVEN PILLARS -->
        <section class="philosophy">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2>The Seven Pillars</h2>
                    <p class="section-sub">A journey from awakening to love</p>
                    <div class="section-divider"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="pillars-grid-3d">
                    <div class="pillar-card">
                        <div class="pillar-number">01</div>
                        <h3>Repent</h3>
                        <p>Change begins with the self. A turning, not guilt. A human being can change.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pillar-card">
                        <div class="pillar-number">02</div>
                        <h3>Presence</h3>
                        <p>Now is the only place anything ever happens. Not the past. Not the future.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pillar-card">
                        <div class="pillar-number">03</div>
                        <h3>Stillness</h3>
                        <p>In the quiet, you meet something steadier than mood or title — simply, "I am."</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pillar-card">
                        <div class="pillar-number">04</div>
                        <h3>Awakening</h3>
                        <p>What we seek is not outside us. It is dormant within, waiting to be awakened.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pillar-card">
                        <div class="pillar-number">05</div>
                        <h3>Know Yourself</h3>
                        <p>See clearly — not who you perform as, but the raw, honest self without flinching.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pillar-card">
                        <div class="pillar-number">06</div>
                        <h3>Fill Your Own Cup</h3>
                        <p>The cup was never empty. The work was never addition. It was recognition.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pillar-card">
                        <div class="pillar-number">07</div>
                        <h3>Love</h3>
                        <p>A full cup exists to pour. To see no distance between self and other — that is love.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- FLOATING QUOTE -->
        <section class="floating-quote">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="quote-content">
                    <blockquote>
                        "You cannot pour from an empty cup — <br>
                        <span class="accent">but yours was never empty to begin with.</span>"
                    </blockquote>
                    <cite>— Mindset.i Philosophy</cite>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SERVICES WITH REAL IMAGES -->
        <section class="services">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2>How We Serve</h2>
                    <p class="section-sub">One philosophy, five rooms of the same house</p>
                    <div class="section-divider"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="services-grid-3d">
                    <!-- The Awakening - Schools -->
                    <div class="service-card-3d">
                        <div class="service-image">
                            <img src="https://kimi-web-img.moonshot.cn/img/thumbs.dreamstime.com/accda230994bf6283e8a55b5b794923e3c645da3.jpg" alt="Students in discussion">
                            <span class="service-tag">Schools</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-body">
                            <h3>The Awakening</h3>
                            <div class="service-price">E4,500 (3hr session)</div>
                            <p>Inspiring students to move from pressure to presence, from performance to self-recognition. A transformative session for young minds ready to see themselves clearly.</p>
                            <a href="/services#schools" class="btn-service">Learn More →</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- The Prefect's Path - Leadership -->
                    <div class="service-card-3d">
                        <div class="service-image">
                            <img src="https://kimi-web-img.moonshot.cn/img/www.shutterstock.com/ba45b7396d1f11186f5b6e6dd51028debb2562c3.jpg" alt="Student leaders">
                            <span class="service-tag">Leadership</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-body">
                            <h3>The Prefect's Path</h3>
                            <div class="service-price">E8,000 (4hr training)</div>
                            <p>Moving student leaders from title to calling — servant leadership through the Seven Pillars. For those who understand that authority is responsibility, not privilege.</p>
                            <a href="/services#prefects" class="btn-service">Learn More →</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- The Full Cup - Teacher Wellness -->
                    <div class="service-card-3d">
                        <div class="service-image">
                            <img src="https://kimi-web-img.moonshot.cn/img/cdn.yogajournal.com/c6a29bbc930243ea3d9f4df13f4ff7026981d8c9.jpg" alt="Teacher wellness">
                            <span class="service-tag">Teacher Wellness</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-body">
                            <h3>The Full Cup</h3>
                            <div class="service-price">E5,000 (staff session)</div>
                            <p>Renewal for educators — because a teacher who has filled their own cup is the only one capable of awakening potential in a classroom. Rest, reflect, return renewed.</p>
                            <a href="/services#teachers" class="btn-service">Learn More →</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- The Bond - Corporate -->
                    <div class="service-card-3d">
                        <div class="service-image">
                            <img src="https://kimi-web-img.moonshot.cn/img/thumbs.dreamstime.com/c909de380544332a314b16caf6016ce46ec54c9f.jpg" alt="Corporate team">
                            <span class="service-tag">Corporate</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-body">
                            <h3>The Bond</h3>
                            <div class="service-price">E15,000+ (team building)</div>
                            <p>Transforming teams through presence, self-knowledge, and the bond of perfection. Programme or full-service. For organisations that understand culture is built one person at a time.</p>
                            <a href="/services#corporate" class="btn-service">Learn More →</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Acceleration Programme - Graduates -->
                    <div class="service-card-3d">
                        <div class="service-image">
                            <img src="https://kimi-web-img.moonshot.cn/img/img.magnific.com/65be08954e07f8cdda2f039b656100c330dc481b.jpg" alt="Graduates celebrating">
                            <span class="service-tag">Acceleration</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-body">
                            <h3>Acceleration Programme</h3>
                            <div class="service-price">E6,000 — E8,500</div>
                            <p>Three programmes: The Emergence (pupils), The Threshold (leavers), The Forge (graduates). Preparing for life beyond school with presence, purpose, and practical wisdom.</p>
                            <a href="/services#acceleration" class="btn-service">Learn More →</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
        <section class="testimonials">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2>What They Say</h2>
                    <p class="section-sub">Voices from schools and organisations we've served</p>
                    <div class="section-divider"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonials-grid">
                    <div class="testimonial-card">
                        <p>"The session was transformative. Our students are still talking about it weeks later. The stillness exercise alone was worth every moment."</p>
                        <div class="author">— Headteacher <span>| Private School</span></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial-card">
                        <p>"I've never seen our prefects so engaged. They left with a sense of purpose, not just a title. This is exactly what leadership development should look like."</p>
                        <div class="author">— Guidance Counsellor <span>| Government School</span></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="testimonial-card">
                        <p>"As a teacher, I came in exhausted. I left renewed. The reminder that my cup is not empty — that I have something to pour — changed my week."</p>
                        <div class="author">— Teacher <span>| High School</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <section class="cta">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Ready to Awaken Potential?</h2>
                <p>Let's talk about how we can serve your school, organisation, or team.</p>
                <a href="/book-now" class="btn-primary">Book a Session →</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>

    <script src="/js/three-bg.js"></script>
</body>
</html>